{"author":"William Newton","message":"fix: use rAF polling for reliable auto-focus during SPA navigation

The previous 100ms setTimeout was unreliable during SPA navigation
because the Select trigger button hadn't rendered yet. Uses
requestAnimationFrame polling (up to ~500ms) to find and focus the
button. Also adds auto-focus to Session Replay Agent's funnel
ChartSelect.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>","sha":"ca1b9b6f74c34240df3926917f8b28ef7499224f"}
{"author":"William Newton","message":"fix: use MutationObserver for reliable auto-focus during SPA navigation

Replace rAF polling with MutationObserver which fires exactly when the
button element appears in the DOM. rAF polling was unreliable during
SPA navigation because it could exhaust attempts before the Select
component committed its trigger button.

